OL,3,CSmall boat arrivals rose in 2025 as
OL,4,Casylum seekers in hotels hit 18-month
OL,5,Clow
OL,7,FSmall boat arrivals to the UK
OL,8,Fincreased by 13% in 2025, while the
OL,9,Fnumber of asylum seekers in hotels has
OL,10,Fhit the lowest level since Labour came
OL,11,Fto power, according to Home Office
OL,12,Ffigures.
OL,14,FThere were 41,000 arrivals on small
OL,15,Fboats, which is 9% below the peak in
OL,16,Fcrossings in 2022, data released on
OL,17,FThursday shows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
