OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772129063
OL,3,CSmall boat arrivals rose in 2025 as
OL,4,Casylum seekers in hotels hit 18-month
OL,5,Clow
OL,7,FThere were 30,657 asylum seekers
OL,8,Fstaying in hotels while they were
OL,9,Fawaiting a decision on their asylum
OL,10,Fclaims at the end of December, 19%
OL,11,Flower than a year earlier.
OL,13,FThe government has pledged to end the
OL,14,Fuse of asylum hotels by the end of
OL,15,Fthis parliament, with an ambition to
OL,16,Fdo so sooner.
OL,18,FThe issue of people being housed in
OL,19,Fhotels rose to prominence last year
OL,20,Fwith protests outside some sites.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
