CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772129063
OL,3,CSmall boat arrivals rose in 2025 as
OL,4,Casylum seekers in hotels hit 18-month
OL,5,Clow
OL,7,FIn October, the government announced
OL,8,Fthat barracks in Scotland and southern
OL,9,FEngland would be used to house around
OL,10,F900 men temporarily as part of
OL,11,Fgovernment efforts to stop using
OL,12,Fhotels as temporary accommodation for
OL,13,Fasylum seekers.
OL,15,FThe number of asylum seekers in hotels
OL,16,Fpeaked at 56,018 at the end of
OL,17,FSeptember 2023 under the then-
OL,18,FConservative government but dropped to
OL,19,Fa record low of 29,561 at the end of
OL,20,FJune 2024 just before the general
OL,21,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
