OL,3,CSmall boat arrivals rose in 2025 as
OL,4,Casylum seekers in hotels hit 18-month
OL,5,Clow
OL,7,FThe backlog of asylum claims has
OL,8,Fdropped sharply to its lowest level in
OL,9,Fmore than five years, while the number
OL,10,Fof people claiming asylum has also
OL,11,Ffallen by 4% on the previous year.
OL,13,FThe data has been published by the
OL,14,FHome Office, which said the figures
OL,15,F"show real progress as we restore
OL,16,Forder and control to our borders".
OL,18,FSome 64,426 people were waiting for an
OL,19,Finitial decision on an asylum
OL,20,Fapplication at the end of December
OL,21,F2025.
