OL,3,CSmall boat arrivals rose in 2025 as
OL,4,Casylum seekers in hotels hit 18-month
OL,5,Clow
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThis is down 20% from 80,841 at the
OL,13,Fend of September 2025, and a drop of
OL,14,Fnearly half (48%) from 124,802 a year
OL,15,Fearlier at the end of December 2024.
OL,17,FThe asylum backlog peaked at 175,457
OL,18,Fat the end of June 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
