OL,3,CSmall boat arrivals rose in 2025 as
OL,4,Casylum seekers in hotels hit 18-month
OL,5,Clow
OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fhave removed nearly 60,000 illegal
OL,9,Fmigrants, numbers in asylum hotels are
OL,10,Fdown, law enforcement action against
OL,11,Fpeople smugglers is at record levels
OL,12,Fand we are bearing down on the asylum
OL,13,Fbacklog.
OL,15,F"But we must go further. The number of
OL,16,Fpeople crossing the Channel is too
OL,17,Fhigh, and too many hotels remain in
OL,18,Fuse.
OL,26,@oD@bOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
