CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772129063
OL,3,CSmall boat arrivals rose in 2025 as
OL,4,Casylum seekers in hotels hit 18-month
OL,5,Clow
OL,7,F"That is why the Home Secretary is
OL,8,Fintroducing sweeping reforms to tackle
OL,9,Fthe pull factors drawing illegal
OL,10,Fmigrants to Britain, and we are
OL,11,Framping up removals of those with no
OL,12,Fright to be here."
OL,14,FThe data released on Thursday also
OL,15,Fshows an increase in the number of
OL,16,Fdetentions and enforced returns.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
